                     CRUSH - Special Edition V0.9
                     ----------------------------
                     
IMPORTANT : When playing from disk, remove write protection, otherwise 
CRUSH will crash !!     
If CRUSH crashes anyway, just reboot and try again - CRUSH is not the
most stable program ever written... but the most cool one :-)
ATTENTION : If CRUSH crashes while saving edited levels, the level-files
may become unreadable. So keep a backuped levelfile (the file LEVELS in
the s-directory of the CRUSH disk), so you can replace the file, if it
is needed. This does not appear very often, just to be sure... ;)


